7da3283c-b2fd-4289-8b97-11c4a2704e4d.text: The ballista is currently being fixed.

2d65a1ce-7f48-4975-8525-0c7c3f6144f5.text: The Khazard stronghold has already been breached.

52d8dd3a-ffad-4220-803d-562f1f02b249.text:
You need to find all three of the tracker
gnomes for the coordinates first.

892c3f41-7ea4-4b44-97f9-88a6207ccad0.text: havent talked to the gnomes yet.

a7f35433-0353-404a-bd30-fe79ed6b8369.text:
That tracker gnome was a bit vague about the x
coordinate! What could it be?

875ec13d-1b25-4590-85d8-302ec73b3cd2.text:
You enter the height and y coordinates you got from the tracker
gnomes.

e4176d00-4c14-49f4-9147-a6c61b1a6589.text: The huge spear completely misses the Khazard stronghold!

cb729b11-8b9d-4be3-bd06-a58c95012172.title: <player>
cb729b11-8b9d-4be3-bd06-a58c95012172.text: Evidently that wasn't the right x coordinate.

60f53578-79bd-4561-b8a3-a62e64f7cb59.text:
You enter the height and y coordinates you got from the tracker
gnomes.

b9a008ba-d7a1-42bc-8647-0209f75b8404.text:
The huge spear flies through the air and screams down directly into
the Khazard stronghold. A deafening crash echoes over the battlefield
as the front entrance is reduced to rubble.
